{"title":"线下教学资源电子使用手册","date":"2018-12-26T09:13:57.000Z","slug":"post","tags":["小学三年级科学下册","第四单元磁铁","线下教学资源电子教程"],"updated":"2019-01-05T08:51:46.180Z","content":"<h4 id=\"电子教程\"><a href=\"#电子教程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"电子教程\"></a><u>电子教程</u></h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">同学们大家好，本次网络学习内容来自浙江教育出版社出版的小学三年级科学第四章磁铁第四节内容，设计者叶钡。</span><br><span class=\"line\">在学习线上内容之前我先来讲解一下本次线下教学资源的使用手册。</span><br><span class=\"line\">在配备的学习资料中，解开资源压缩包之后，点击story.swf进入课件首页。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005FZoJFly1fyvrj4qvvhj30g404mjrm.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">进入首页，点击开始学习按钮，进入下一页【所有按钮都会有状态的变化】</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005FZoJFly1fyvrtz14j6j309i073mxe.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">这张内容，目的在于回顾第四章磁铁第三节相关内容，为第四节做准备。了解完毕之后点击小黄人进入下一页。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005FZoJFly1fyvrtz3yfoj30ae07tq3f.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">本张内容引入“悬停法”，点击问号按钮出现答案。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005FZoJFly1fyvrtz735tj309i076dg6.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">本张内容引入“悬停法”，点击问号按钮出现答案。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005FZoJFly1fyvrtz735tj309i076dg6.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">点击“悬挂的磁铁”可以跳转到练习题，点击“小黄人”进入小结页面。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005FZoJFly1fyvrtzb83hj309j073t94.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">点击左侧小黄人进入小结页面，点击右侧小黄人，回到上一界面。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005FZoJFly1fyvrtzdavkj309i073wew.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">这张内容，点击中间三个按钮，会一次出现三句总结语。点击”小黄人“进入下一界面。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005FZoJFly1fyvrtzhfqlj309h074q3d.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">点击下方小黄人可以对应知道1-4号磁铁实验的答案，点击上方小黄人，进入下一页。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005FZoJFly1fyvs0x14alj309h06zgm1.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">点击左侧小黄人，进入下一页，点击右侧小黄人返回上一页。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005FZoJFly1fyvs0x44rfj309e072dg9.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">点击下方小黄人会出现相应的磁铁形状，点击上方小黄人分别返回上一页和进入下一页。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005FZoJFly1fyvs0x7dlrj309k073mxh.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">点击左侧第一个磁铁出现第一个科普小知识，点击上方小黄人分别返回上一页和进入下一页。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005FZoJFly1fyvs0xasikj309j0733yy.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">点击下方磁铁按钮，出现第二个小科普。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005FZoJFly1fyvs0xd5k8j309k078gm3.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">四个对话框会一次出现，为上课内容的总结，记得仔细看，右侧“再学一次”按钮可以回到目录页，进行再次学习。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/005FZoJFly1fyvs0xifb4j309h07a3yz.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p></div>\n<p><u>好啦，知道怎么操作线下资源了之后，就来了解一下线上学习吧。</u></p>\n","prev":{"title":"课程计划——学习之前请阅读","slug":"post1"},"next":{"title":"5.磁铁的相互作用力之课外拓展","slug":"unit5"},"link":"http://yoursite.com/post/post/","reward":true}